son, is abnormal in Florida, a state where it=E2=80=99s rarely cold, though=
 they did get a freak snowstorm this year. Florida is solidly red at this p=
oint, sure, but why wouldn=E2=80=99t its 4.8 million registered
Democrats <em>also </em>feel the blues that have allegedly impacted other s=
tates? And sure, red-staters might like pink, but so do blue staters: It=E2=
=80=99s an industry-wide phenomenon.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:=
0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Nevertheless, the =
